comments: Mitchell (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Hyland (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) avoids making contact with Monk (SAC) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) is already in Sabonis' (SAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Hyland (DEN) and Mitchell (SAC) come together at the same spot and incidental foot to foot contact occurs on the perimeter.
Sabonis (SAC) moves somewhat towards Jokic (DEN) and marginal body contact occurs as Jokic secures the pass.
Jokic (DEN) is already in Mitchell's (SAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Lyles (SAC) legally contests Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Braun (DEN) brings his hands towards Sabonis (SAC) and marginal contact occurs as Braun releases from the contact.
Sabonis (SAC) rolls towards the basket and marginal contact occurs with Braun (DEN) as Braun goes under the pick.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Braun (DEN) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) and Jokic (DEN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Mitchell's (SAC) path and does not deliver contact as Mitchell goes under the pick.
Sabonis (SAC) lowers his arm down and makes contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm, which affects Jokic's driving shot attempt.
Lyles (SAC) is firming up over his left foot and absorbs the contact from Caldwell-Pope (DEN) to his upper body.
Jokic (DEN) is moving alongside Lyles' (SAC) path and absorbs the contact as Lyles cuts back towards the basket.
Sabonis (SAC) swipes his arm down and makes contact with Jokic's (DEN) arm that causes Jokic to lose control of the ball.
Lyles' (SAC) right foot is out of bounds when he makes contact with the ball.
Jokic (DEN) brushes Sabonis' (SAC) arm as he defends the shot near the rim, and the contact is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) and Jokic (DEN) briefly engage and disengage off ball
Hyland (DEN) pulls Fox's (SAC) jersey away from his body and restricts his ability to defend the pass.
Lyles (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball, dislodging the ball from Braun (DEN) as he defends the shot near the rim, and any ensuing arm contact is marginal.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) is moving alongside Fox's (SAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during Fox's drive.
Fox (SAC) overtly and abruptly veers into Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and delivers contact that dislodges him from his legally obtained defensive position.
Sabonis (SAC) and Jokic (DEN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Jokic (DEN) is already in Mitchell's (SAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Mitchell (SAC) brushes Hyland's (DEN) arm and marginal contact occurs as Hyland passes the ball.
Sabonis (SAC) turns towards Jokic (DEN) and marginal body contact occurs after Jokic has released his jump shot attempt.
Monk (SAC) brings his forearm towards Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) side and marginal contact occurs as Monk turns towards the baseline.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) swipes his arm down and makes simultaneous contact with the ball and Monk's (SAC) arm as he defends the shot.
Porter Jr. (DEN) and Barnes (SAC) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Jokic (DEN) brings his hands towards Fox (SAC) and marginal contact occurs as Jokic releases away to receive the pass.
Fox (SAC) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
